HEADWORD: Aragonite
<hw>A*rag"o*nite</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[From
<etsep>Aragon</etsep>, in Spain.]</ety> <fld>(Min.)</fld> <def>A mineral
